data.description: Nestled within a quiet cul-de-sac, this charming home boasts an expansive nearly acre-sized lot and has fresh paint on both its interior and exterior. The family room welcomes you with its vaulted ceilings and an inviting fireplace, creating a cozy ambiance. Seamless transitions lead to the dining area and a spacious kitchen appointed with white cabinets, a delightful breakfast nook, and new appliances including a stove and dishwasher. The main floor encompasses three bedrooms and two full baths, with the primary bedroom and dining area offering access to a generous second-story deck. The lower level unfolds with a fully-equipped basement featuring a separate kitchen and full bath, complemented by a private entrance from the garage and an external entry to the lower deck and expansive backyard. Don't miss this fantastic opportunity to own a perfect home with NO HOA!
